            <title>[SOLR-3757] Add coment in solrConfig.xml about master/slave SolrReplication</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3757</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should add a notification that if we would use master/slave replication we should comment the SolrCloud replicationHandler in the solrConfig.xml file.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;requestHandler name=&quot;/replication&quot; class=&quot;solr.ReplicationHandler&quot; startup=&quot;lazy&quot; /&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;else it will overload the replication handler.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
